data.description: Welcome to this charming two-story home nestled in the heart of San Antonio, TX. As you step inside, you are greeted by the warmth of wood and tile floors that seamlessly flow throughout the entire residence. Fully paid solar panel system included. To your right, the dining room beckons, effortlessly transitioning into the inviting living room. The living space boasts a unique touch with a small bar area featuring a sink, perfect for entertaining, and an adjacent library for quiet reading or work. Around the corner awaits the breakfast area and a well-appointed galley kitchen, providing a delightful space for culinary endeavors. The main level strategically houses the primary bedroom, ensuring a private retreat away from the main living areas. Venture upstairs to discover the remaining bedrooms and a full bathroom, offering comfortable accommodations for guests. The thoughtful layout provides a sense of separation, balancing shared spaces with private quarters. Step outside into the backyard oasis, where a sunroom beckons you to relax and enjoy the picturesque view of the lush grassed expanse and the inviting inground pool. Additional bedroom in the backyard is not included in the total sq ft of the property. This outdoor haven is perfect for hosting gatherings or simply unwinding in the tranquility of your own private retreat. With its convenient location and well-designed layout, this San Antonio gem is ready to welcome you home.
